    div className = "social-container" >
    <
    div className = "social-facebook-container" >

    a href = "https://www.facebook.com/kasunjith.satanarachchi"
    className = "social-facebook"
    target = "_blank"
    rel = "noopener noreferrer" >

    FontAwesomeIcon icon = { faFacebook }
    size = "2x" / >
    <
    /a> <
    /div> <
    div className = "social-twitter-container" >

    size = "2x" / >

    /a> <
    /div> <
    div className = "social-linkedin-container" >

    a href = "https://www.linkedin.com/in/kasunjith-satanarachchi-15a059bb/"
    className = "social-facebook"
    target = "_blank"
    rel = "noopener noreferrer" >
    <
    FontAwesomeIcon icon = { faLinkedin }
    size = "2x" / >
    <
    /a> <
    /div> <
    /div>

);

export default Social
